{"id": 2739, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些时刻你突然意识到，自己变得越来越像爸妈了？", "description": "比如，开始爱上穿羊绒衫了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3852, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190115113639Ha7Z96oM4ChIeYXV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-22T03:00:38Z", "options": [{"id": 323840, "content": "在一些事上理解父母的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491715}, {"id": 323843, "content": "感觉多喝饮料，多吃垃圾食品就会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561336}, {"id": 323844, "content": "意识到性感中不好的东西\n且无力改变", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564189}, {"id": 323846, "content": "每当胖了10斤看着自己的大脸盘穿着老妈的睡衣素颜站在镜子面前嘴微笑的时候仿佛看见了我妈😀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564670}, {"id": 323847, "content": "晚上睡觉前，会像我妈一样检查门是否关好了，出门前检查煤气是否关好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564681}, {"id": 324103, "content": "人生轨迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386990}, {"id": 323848, "content": "吃饭包尾清盘底", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564690}, {"id": 323849, "content": "臭脾气\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964637}, {"id": 323850, "content": "穿西装而且穿秋裤了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044028}, {"id": 323851, "content": "没什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551281}, {"id": 323852, "content": "脾气某天开始变得暴躁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823572}, {"id": 323853, "content": "羊绒衫真的很舒服啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751118}, {"id": 323854, "content": "有工作了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538425}, {"id": 323855, "content": "唠叨在乎的人早点睡，劝她多喝热水；天一冷，就穿的厚厚的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525407}, {"id": 324111, "content": "早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397575}, {"id": 323600, "content": "和对象吵架的时候，发现自己也会像爸妈一样歇斯底里或是逃避问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 173, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323856, "content": "嗯，说话时候的神态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465784}, {"id": 323602, "content": "对喜欢的人好的方式，不自觉地和爸妈一样，唠叨着让对方吃早饭穿秋裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 418, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323858, "content": "突然觉得香菜芹菜都挺好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127093}, {"id": 324114, "content": "不再乱发脾气了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563080}, {"id": 323603, "content": "回到家里看着电视在沙发上睡着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323859, "content": "看着那些孩子在放炮竹，只觉得危险，不觉得好玩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198394}, {"id": 323860, "content": "大学的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20190122154152WYeV4HDfytkOLo37.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564171}, {"id": 323861, "content": "不知不觉说起养生知识和食疗一套一套的，什么东西清热去火，什么食物补血补气，冷感冒发汗，热感冒降火…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 324117, "content": "貌似我对新事物的接受能力变低了，有点开始怀旧了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564864}, {"id": 323862, "content": "现在真的老了，但是很喜欢很喜欢羊毛衫 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20190122154253Mc4wbUpiVEKqk5yN.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564171}, {"id": 323863, "content": "开始像父母一样开始唠叨人开始为自己在意的人花钱买衣服开始多喝水思考方式越来越像老年人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538092}, {"id": 323864, "content": "看动画片的时候会发呆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538603}, {"id": 324120, "content": "觉得皮鞋很帅气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447384}, {"id": 323865, "content": "记性越来越不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564773}, {"id": 323866, "content": "开始找秋裤穿的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564780}, {"id": 323868, "content": "开始腰疼腿疼了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504532}, {"id": 325661, "content": "某些时候脱口而出一些话.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566906}, {"id": 323870, "content": "开始头疼弟弟的功课，觉得这孩子怎么这么不听话，然后忽然发现重复的都是当年被教育的那些话", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560854}, {"id": 323871, "content": "节俭的美德", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}, {"id": 323872, "content": "二十二岁已经开始注重养生了(,,•́.•̀,,)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564791}, {"id": 323873, "content": "心态老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145761}, {"id": 322850, "content": "朋友来家里看猫，会让猫展示各种绝活，才发现自己也是会让小孩子在客人面前背唐诗的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 249, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323874, "content": "磨磨叨叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197116}, {"id": 323876, "content": "开始认真洗蔬菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328523}, {"id": 323877, "content": "好好套被套", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328523}, {"id": 324133, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565847}, {"id": 323878, "content": "钱不够花了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488474}, {"id": 324134, "content": "啦啦啦啦咯哦哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565847}, {"id": 323879, "content": "爱喝咖啡了，之前只觉得苦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556565}, {"id": 324135, "content": "有一天穿了两条秋裤😱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277378}, {"id": 323880, "content": "喝白开水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384546}, {"id": 323881, "content": "愿意抽出时间锻炼身体", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294922}, {"id": 323882, "content": "羊绒衫，还有丝巾，以前没感觉，现在有点懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213034}, {"id": 323883, "content": "东西挑便宜的买，货比三家\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543383}]}